data.description: Charming Fixer-Upper! Take advantage of this unique opportunity to own a single-story home in San Antonio, offered at a value below the typical market rate. Perfect for those looking to add a personal touch, this home requires some TLC care to truly shine. The interior offers concrete flooring throughout the main living areas, providing a durable and easy-to-maintain surface. The kitchen is a functional space with granite countertops and includes a stove and a breakfast area. Additionally, there's a separate dining room that offers versatility and can be adapted to your needs, whether it's a home office, craft room, or an extra living space. The primary bedroom is located at the back of the house for added privacy and features a full bathroom. Both bathrooms in the home have received some updates. An eco-friendly addition, the home comes with solar panels, which will be fully paid off at closing, offering energy savings for the new homeowner. While the home does not have a garage (home was built without one), it includes a convenient parking pad. This home presents a wonderful chance for buyers in San Antonio to create a space that truly reflects their style and needs.
